{"tid":2310023,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"譚得志涉煽動文字案交國安指定法官決定是否涉國安法","createTime":"2020-12-03T03:25:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-03T03:39:32.000Z","uid":193380,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dfdef95a8bd465c9d1078c5a03bdbb05da411604","tid":2310023,"uid":193380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T03:25:13.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】人民力量譚得志被控發表煽動文字等14項控罪，由國安法指定法官決定案件是否牽涉危害國家安全。<br />\n<br />\n譚得志由囚車押抵區域法院，案件改由法官陳廣池處理。他在庭上證實自己屬國安法下，其中一名指定區域法院法官。他強調處理是次申請時，不會觸及任何本案以外議題，又指有能力及有權處理案件。他要求控辯雙方討論，是否合併處理。<br />\n<br />\n譚得志現時所面對三宗案件，合共14項控罪及開審日期，又指國安法以中文審訊為主，案中證據包括口號等亦以廣東話說出，即時傳譯或失去部分含意，提議以廣東話審理，交由控辯雙方決定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=415188\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D415188&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPb2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=64f8da8e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D415188&h=3feaa430\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=415188</a>"},{"pid":"0ea9c2db80a1c2e27d17a49c5c9898a3fd777545","tid":2310023,"uid":66324,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T03:28:04.000Z","msg":"周家明<br />\n李運騰<br />\n陳廣池<br />\n蘇惠德<br />\n<br />\n仲有邊三個"},{"pid":"85228ac057f11176112773d369f2106b675124ba","tid":2310023,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T03:29:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d9e2672f8ee03a098e5fdbf6d9cde2f699be526","tid":2310023,"uid":184261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ea9c2db80a1c2e27d17a49c5c9898a3fd777545","tid":2310023,"uid":66324,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T03:28:04.000Z","msg":"周家明<br />\n李運騰<br />\n陳廣池<br />\n蘇惠德<br />\n<br />\n仲有邊三個"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T03:37:54.000Z","msg":"嚴舜儀 徐綺薇 蘇文隆"},{"pi